{"word":"H5483 - סוּס - çûwç - soos - Crane","slug":"H5483","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">סוּס</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>çûwç"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Crane"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E1;&#x05E1;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E1;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05E1; - su&#x0302;s  su&#x0302;s</b> - <i>soos, soos</i><p/>From an unused root meaning to <i>skip</i> (properly for joy); a <i>horse</i> (as leaping); also a <i>swallow</i> (from its rapid <i>flight</i>): - crane, horse ([-back, -hoof]). Compare <a href=\"#/H6571\">H6571</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4534\">H4534</a>, <a href=\"#/H5482\">H5482</a>, <a href=\"#/H5484\">H5484</a>, <a href=\"#/H5485\">H5485</a>, <a href=\"#/H5526\">H5526</a>"}]}